@Node "Installation" "IconAppearer.guide/Installation"

Installation

Simply copy "IconAppearer" to your SYS:WBStartup - Drawer and reboot
your system. That's it ;-)

@EndNode

@Node "Program Usage" "Program Usage"
@Toc "Main"

Program Usage

Since there are currently no parameters for "IconAppearer", simply
start it or let it be.

