@Node "Internals" "Internals"

   Internals

IconAppearer patches some functions of the dos.library to discover
changes of icon files. The functions patched are:
Open(), OpenFromLock(), Close(), Rename(), DeleteFile().
When an icon file is changed a private workbench.library
call is used to notify the workbench. 

Because of the above patches some virus-killers may think IconAppearer
is a virus but it isn't.

@EndNode



@Node "EventWare" "EventWare"

   EventWare

IconAppearer is EventWare.  That means, if you use it for more than 2
weeks, try to get a copy of my program Event!  (currently version 1.2) and
register it.

If you have already registered Event!  take this program as a gift from the
author.

When you register please don't forget to mention the keyword IconAppearer.

You may filerequest Event!  from my boss:  amiganet#39:171/207 with the
magic EVENT.  It is also available for ftp as event12.lha (53784 bytes).


@EndNode


